experiment KAIRADIO
instrument VHF
start 2013 03 21 0900
end 2013 03 21 1300
status R
description Heating, KAIRA  measurements and VHF
contact Antti Kero
email antti.kero@sgo.fi
operator Antti Kero
submitter Carl-Fredrik Enell
resources FI(16)
notes
Common volume measurements in the D-region ionosphere with the KAIRA  
riometer (45 deg. tilted beam) and the EISCAT VHF radar (vertical).
Ionospheric opacity is altered by active on/off HF heating. We  
anticipate to see the heating effect within one single experiment.
